description: Tailwind v4, PostCSS, and global styles
globs: src/style.css,src/components/**/*.scss,postcss.config.js,gatsby-browser.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

# Styling

- Tailwind v4: `@import "tailwindcss"` and `@source` in `src/style.css` (no `tailwind.config.js`).
- PostCSS plugin: `@tailwindcss/postcss` in `postcss.config.js`.
- Component SCSS only in `layout.scss`; prefer Tailwind utilities in TSX.
- Prism CSS imported in `gatsby-browser.ts` for code blocks.

When adding templates/components with new class names, ensure their paths are covered by `@source` in `src/style.css`.
